    <item>
      <title>科技股受拖累、中国股市波动，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市下跌，而中国股市在周四新闻发布会前出现波动，该发布会可能会详细介绍支持该国陷入困境的房地产行业的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 22:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济放缓之际，全球两大铁矿石生产商仍提高产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/rio-tinto-s-iron-ore-shipments-edges-up-1-guidance-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国尚未解决的房地产危机导致铁矿石需求面临阻力，但全球两大铁矿石供应商力拓集团和淡水河谷公司上季度仍提高了铁矿石产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/rio-tinto-s-iron-ore-shipments-edges-up-1-guidance-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 21:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
